      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that perfectly balances performance and practicality. Mechanically, it is in excellent shape; the engine pulls strong, the transmission shifts smoothly, and I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records. The interior is clean and smoke-free, featuring supple leather seats with only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. While the exterior paint retains a deep gloss, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side alloy wheel, consistent with regular use. All electronics, from the navigation system to the heated seats, are fully operational. This is a reliable, turn-key car ready for its next owner.",
